Ah yes, the old IPL switch... quite an advance
over memorizing the octal machine code of
the bootstrap loader and toggling it in on
the front panel switches.
I got really fast on bringing up a PDP-8 :-)
IIRC, the 360/370 family has a complete other
assembly code for programming the I/O Channel,
separate from BAL-360 code.
